milestones.description: Haseeb Amjad and Ankur Vasishta's 29-run partnership is HKG's highest for the 7th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 24 between Najeeb Amar and Munir Dar
Nadeem Ahmed has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (5) for HKG, going past Afzaal Haider
Irfan Ahmed has become the top wicket-taker for HKG in ODIs with 5 wickets, going past Ilyas Gull's 4
Babar Hayat has broken the record for most sixes (3) in ODIs for HKG, going past Irfan Ahmed's 2
